109. $y=\cfrac{x^2-10x+24}{|x-7|+|x-3|-2}=\begin{cases}
\cfrac{(x-6)(x-4)}{7-x+3-x-2}=\cfrac{6-x}{2},\ x<3,\\
\cfrac{(x-6)(x-4)}{7-x+x-3-2}=\cfrac{x^2-10x+24}{2},\ 3\leqslant x \leqslant 7,\\
\cfrac{(x-6)(x-4)}{x-7+x-3-2}=\cfrac{x-4}{2},\ 7<x.\end{cases}$
